node.text: Ad - I collaborated with @wacom and got to try the Wacom One. I were suppose to get it in May for @mermay_official, but due to Covid and living in Kenya I got it a bit late. Please forgive the quality - I like drawing more than doing videos 💕 @wacom

node.text:
Here’s the video of my process for my @imagineFX cover (if you wish to see it in real time check it out on their YouTube channel: https://youtu.be/KF_Ektb4fQ8). I hope you’ll find this informative and that it might help to inspire in these uninspiring days.
#staysafe #stayhome  #girlsinanimation

node.text:
A free weekend means time to do some #gouache #painting. I hope you enjoy! #girlsinanimation 
Paints: @holbeinartistmaterials #gouache 
Paper: @archespapers 300g hot pressed

node.text:
Looking back at old work 👠 while I’m
enjoying my last few weeks here in Denmark before I go back to Kenya and start up work again. I enjoy being home but I can’t wait to be back and to start up work full time and drawing again. I’ve missed it so much! #girlsinanimation

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by PERNILLE ØRUM | Vis Dev on August 18, 2021. May be an illustration.

node.text:
Check out what finally arrive at my door today 💜🧜‍♀️
My #mermaidsinmay2 for approval. It turned out so nice and I’m excited to get the copies out to everyone who preordered this book earlier in the year. It’ll still take a few weeks before shipping but we’re getting close! 

Unfortunately I’ll not have anymore available at this time if you did not preorder the book…

#mermay #girlsinanimation #mermaid

node.text: Did my first talk in over a year at @armand_serrano’s amazingly orchestrated @iconmanila. I was honored to be amongst such great artists and had so much fun. Ended it with a very quick demo of #color and #reference. #girlsinanimation #characterdesign

node.text:
Small summer challenge ☀️
Found this #gustavklimt inspired sketch I never finished. I think I’ll give it a go soon, but until I do I’d love to see how you’d color it (even draw it in your style).
And please tag me and use #ctiysPernilleKlimt so I can see it. 
NB: no deadline.

#girlsinanimation #challenge
